      ],
      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif\"><span dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">A 55 years old male accident victim in casualty urgently needs blood. The blood bank is unable to determine his ABO group, as his red cell group and plasma group do not match. Emergency transfusion of the patient should be with:</span></span></span></span></p>",
      "unique_key": "Q5809961",
