      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">A 58-year-old man with a history of hemophilia A requires a blood product transfusion during a surgical procedure. </span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">ABO incompatibility is not seen with:</span></span></span></span></p>",
